citation: Inland Fisheries (Seasons and Waters) Amendment Order 2014 (Rescinded) (Tas)
text:
Inland Fisheries (Seasons and Waters) Amendment Order 2014 (Rescinded)

This Statutory Rule has been rescinded.

1. (Rescinded)
    The Inland Fisheries (Seasons and Waters) Amendment Order 2014 have been rescinded by Schedule 3 to the Redundant Legislation Repeal Act 2016
